  "remarks": "TAi.038, Title: a) Maulavi b) Mullah. Designation: a) Governor of Khost and Paktika provinces under the Taliban regime b) Vice-Minister of Information and Culture under the Taliban regime c) Consulate Dept., Ministry of Foreign Affairs under the Taliban regime. Believed to be in the Afghanistan/Pakistan border area. Taliban member responsible for Nangarhar Province as at 2009. Until 7 Sept. 2007 he was also listed under number TI.A.48.01. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822(2008) was concluded on 1 Jun. 2010; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 23 February 2001 (amended on 7 Sept 2007, 21 Sep. 2007, 29 Nov 2011 and 13 Aug 2012)",
